@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eestlk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (v1 * wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.24)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.70 + tmp + 0.81)) + v0)
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.26 * v0 + 0.58)) / wp.cos((v1 + 0.11 + v1 + 0.55)))
    v1 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.27 / v1 + 0.79) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.95)))
    data[tid] = v0
